                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Eh ! quel est en effet mon père ?\nCelui qui m'instruit, qui m'éclaire,\nDont le secours m'est assuré ;\nEt celui dont le cœur oublie\nLes biens répandus sur sa vie,\nC'est là le fils dénaturé."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Ingrats, monstres que la nature",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "A pétris d'une fange impure",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Qu'elle dédaigna d'animer,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Il manque à votre âme sauvage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Des humains le plus beau partage ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Vous n'avez pas le don d'aimer.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ingrats, monstres que la nature\nA pétris d'une fange impure\nQu'elle dédaigna d'animer,\nIl manque à votre âme sauvage\nDes humains le plus beau partage ;\nVous n'avez pas le don d'aimer."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Nous admirons le fier courage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Du lion fumant de carnage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Symbole du dieu des combats.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "D'où vient que l'univers déteste",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "La couleuvre bien moins funeste ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Elle est l'image des ingrats.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Nous admirons le fier courage\nDu lion fumant de carnage,\nSymbole du dieu des combats.\nD'où vient que l'univers déteste\nLa couleuvre bien moins funeste ?\nElle est l'image des ingrats."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Quel monstre plus hideux s'avance ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "La Nature fuit et s'offense",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "A l'aspect de ce vieux giton ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Il a la rage de Zoïle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "De Gacon l'esprit et le style,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Et l'âme impure de Chausson.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quel monstre plus hideux s'avance ?\nLa Nature fuit et s'offense\nA l'aspect de ce vieux giton ;\nIl a la rage de Zoïle,\nDe Gacon l'esprit et le style,\nEt l'âme impure de Chausson."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "C'est Desfontaines, c'est ce prêtre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Venu de Sodome à Bicêtre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "De Bicêtre au sacré vallon :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "A-t-il l'espérance bizarre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Que le bûcher qu'on lui prépare",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Soit fait des lauriers d'Apollon ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est Desfontaines, c'est ce prêtre\nVenu de Sodome à Bicêtre,\nDe Bicêtre au sacré vallon :\nA-t-il l'espérance bizarre\nQue le bûcher qu'on lui prépare\nSoit fait des lauriers d'Apollon ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Il m'a dû l'honneur et la vie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Et, dans son ingrate furie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "De Rousseau lâche imitateur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Avec moins d'art et plus d'audace,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "De la fange où sa voix coasse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Il outrage son bienfaiteur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il m'a dû l'honneur et la vie,\nEt, dans son ingrate furie,\nDe Rousseau lâche imitateur,\nAvec moins d'art et plus d'audace,\nDe la fange où sa voix coasse\nIl outrage son bienfaiteur."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Qu'un Hibernois, loin de la France,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Aille ensevelir dans Bysance",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Sa honte à l'abri du croissant ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "D'un œil tranquille et sans colère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Je vois son crime et sa misère ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Il n'emporte que mon argent.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Qu'un Hibernois, loin de la France,\nAille ensevelir dans Bysance\nSa honte à l'abri du croissant ;\nD'un œil tranquille et sans colère,\nJe vois son crime et sa misère ;\nIl n'emporte que mon argent."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Mais l'ingrat dévoré d'envie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Trompette de la calomnie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Qui cherche à flétrir mon honneur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Voilà le ravisseur coupable,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Voilà le larcin détestable",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Dont je dois punir la noirceur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais l'ingrat dévoré d'envie,\nTrompette de la calomnie,\nQui cherche à flétrir mon honneur,\nVoilà le ravisseur coupable,\nVoilà le larcin détestable\nDont je dois punir la noirceur."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Pardon, si ma main vengeresse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Sur ce monstre un moment s'abaisse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "A lancer ces utiles traits,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Et si de la douce peinture",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "De ta vertu brillante et pure",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Je passe à ces sombres portraits.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pardon, si ma main vengeresse\nSur ce monstre un moment s'abaisse\nA lancer ces utiles traits,\nEt si de la douce peinture\nDe ta vertu brillante et pure\nJe passe à ces sombres portraits."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Mais lorsque Virgile et le Tasse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Ont chanté dans leur noble audace",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Les dieux de la terre et des mers,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Leur muse, que le ciel inspire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Ouvre le ténébreux empire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Et peint les monstres des enfers.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais lorsque Virgile et le Tasse\nOnt chanté dans leur noble audace\nLes dieux de la terre et des mers,\nLeur muse, que le ciel inspire,\nOuvre le ténébreux empire,\nEt peint les monstres des enfers."
        }
